{
  "chapter": 54,
  "chapter_summary": "上官金虹与荆无命在金钱帮总部工作，有人求见。上官金虹下令杀死来者及其引荐人向松，荆无命却因来者是个残废孩子而未动手。来者竟是龙啸云之子龙小云，虽年幼却老成阴辣，提出以李寻欢的性命换取其父与上官金虹结拜。上官金虹起初不屑一顾，但龙小云以小李飞刀例不虚发为由，指出上官金虹并无十足把握亲手杀死李寻欢，又以龙啸云可为臂助为诱饵，最终打动上官金虹。荆无命主动请缨护送。上官金虹看出龙小云阴辣狠毒，指出若非李寻欢已废其武功，二十年后此子便可与自己争雄，暗藏杀机。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一七九。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "有人求见帮主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "他不肯说出姓名。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "为什么事求见？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "他要等见到帮主之面时才肯说出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "人在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "就在前院。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "杀了他！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "人是谁带来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "第八舵主向松。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "text": "连向松一起杀！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_qi_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "一七九",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我去！",
      "tone": "果断",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "去！向松若未还手，送他家属黄金万两；向松若还手，灭他满门。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我没有杀他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "世人皆可杀，他为何不能杀？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我不杀孩子。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你说，要见我的人只是个孩子？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "带他进来！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "晚辈龙小云，参见帮主。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "龙小云？龙啸云是你的什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "家父。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "是你父亲叫你来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "他自己为何不来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "家父若来求见，非但未能见帮主之面，而且还可能有杀身之祸。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你认为我不会杀你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "三尺童子，性命早已悬于帮主指掌之间，帮主非不能杀，义不尪杀！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你年纪虽小，身体虽弱，胆子倒不小。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "一个人若有所求，无论谁的胆子都会大的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "你只听他说话，能听得出他是个孩子么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我没有听。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "不说话，是你最大的长处，不听人说话，却可能是你的致命伤。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你们求的是什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "每件事都有很多种说法，晚辈本也可将此事说得委婉些，但帮主日理万机，晚辋不敢多扰，只能选择最直接的说法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "很好，对付说话嘤嗠的人，我只有一种法子，那就是将他的舔子割下来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "晚辈此来，只是要和帮主谈一笔交易。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "交易？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "以前也有人和我谈过交易，你可愿知道我对付他们的法子？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "晚辈在听着。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我对付他们，也只有一种法子，乱刀分尸！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "但这交易却和别人不同，否则晚辈也不敢来了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "交易就是交易，有何不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这交易对帮主有百利而无一害。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "帮主威震天下，富可敌国，世上所有的东西，帮主侥可予取予求。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "确是如此，所以我根本不必和人谈交易。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "但世上还是有样东西，帮主未必能得到。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这样东西本身价值也许并不高，但在帮主说来，就不同了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "因为世上只有得不到的东西，才最珍贵。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你说那是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "李寻欢的命！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "李寻欢的命已在我们掌握之中，只要帮主愿意，晚辉随时可将他奉上。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "李寻欢何足道哉？我根本就从未将他放在眼里。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "既是如此，晚辈告退。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "慢着。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "帮主还有何分嘉？",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你想以李寻欢的命来换什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "家父久慕帮主声名，只恨无缘识荆。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "这是废话，我只想听你要求的是什么？",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "家父但求能在天下英雄面前，与帮主结为八拜之交。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "看来龙啸云倒也不欧是个聪明人，只可惜这件事却做得太笨了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这种做法的确很笨，但最笨的法子，往往最有效。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你有把握这交易能谈成？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "若无把握，晚辈何必冒死而来？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "龙啸云只有你这一个独子，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "既是如此，他就不该要你来的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这只因若是换了别人前来，根本无法见到帮主之面。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你们本是交易的买主，但你一来，情况就变了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "帮主认为可以用我来要挟家父，逼他交出李寻欢来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "帮主素有知人之明，但对家父，却看错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "难道他宁可让我杀了你，也不肯交出李寻欢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "难道他不是人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是人，但人却有很多种。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "他是哪一种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "家父和帮主正是同样的一种人，为了达到目的，不择一切手段，也不惜牵牵牵一切。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "近二十年来，已没有人敢在我面前说这种话了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "就因为帮主是这种人，是以晚辉才敢说这种话，也只有这种话，才能打动帮主这种人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我若不答应，你们难道就要放了李寻欢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你不怕他杀了你们复仇？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他是另一种人，绝不会做这种事的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "他若会做这种事，遭遇也不会有今日之悲惨。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你们纵然放了他，又怎知我不能亲手杀他？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "小李飞刀，例不虚发。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你认为连我也躲不过他的那一刀？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "至少帮主并没有十分的把握，是么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "千金之子，坐不垂堂，以帮主现在的身份地位，又何必冒这个险？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "何况，家父武功虽不甚高，但声望地位、心计机智，都不在别人之下，帮主与他结为兄弟，也是有利而无害的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "李寻欢也是他的兄弟，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "他既能出卖了李寻欢，又怎知不会出卖我？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "因为帮主不是李寻欢。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "不错，龙啸云就算有胆子敢出卖我，也没有那么大的本事。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "帮主答应了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "我怎知李寻欢已在你们掌握之中？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "只要帮主发出请帖，邀请天下英雄来参与家父与帮主结拜之盛典……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你认为他们敢来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "来不来都不重要，只要大家都知道这件事就行了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你考虑得倒很周到。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这件事帮主也许还要考虑，晚辈就落脚在城中的如云客栈，等候帮主的消息。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "只要帮主请帖发出，有人收到，晚辉随时都可将李寻欢带到帮主这里来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "带到这里来？……哿，你父子只怕还没有这么大的本事。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "这点晚辈自然也知道，连少林心眉大师和田七爷都做不到的事，晚辈自然更做不到了，只不过……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "不过怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "一路上若有荆先生护送，就可万无一失了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "荆无命",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "我去。",
      "tone": "枝枝",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_jing_wu_ming",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你武功已被废，永难复澈，下手的人又是李寻欢！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "你恨他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "沉重",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_jin_hong",
      "speaker_name": "上官金虹",
      "listener": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "text": "其实你非但不诨恨他，还该感激他才是。",
      "tone": "冷淡",
      "chapter": 54,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_xiao_yun",
      "speaker_name": "龙小云",
